 that Verant has, yet they haven't come close... and in the foreseeable future, they won't.  Most of you guys sound as if you're obsessed with Verant, that you expected them to provide you with a lifestyle... an online gaming life.  It's a freaking game.  I played EQ for 6 months, hours on hours every day, rarely missing a day... and loved it while i did... certainly it was the most time i ever spent on a game. EQ is a game.  SB is a game.  Get over it.  Pathetic morons like you are the reasons why i don't visit MMOG forums, you expect these games to be a lifestyle.
